            <title><![CDATA[#深圳控烟进行时# 【[话筒]深圳控烟第2弹现场！罗湖2名摊主被罚】4月4日上午10时许，由深圳市控烟办、深圳市慢性病防治中心，深圳市市场监管局罗湖监管局等工作...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%B7%B1%E5%9C%B3%E6%8E%A7%E7%83%9F%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E6%97%B6%23&amp;extparam=%23%E6%B7%B1%E5%9C%B3%E6%8E%A7%E7%83%9F%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E6%97%B6%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#深圳控烟进行时#</span></a> 【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>深圳控烟第2弹现场！罗湖2名摊主被罚】4月4日上午10时许，由深圳市控烟办、深圳市慢性病防治中心，深圳市市场监管局罗湖监管局等工作人员组成的督查组来到罗湖区富宝东门市场，开展第二场农贸（集贸、批发）市场控烟督查！现场2名吸烟摊主被罚！快和小卫一起看现场👇🏻<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%B7%B1%E5%9C%B3%E6%8E%A7%E7%83%9F%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#深圳控烟#</span></a><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%B7%B1%E5%9C%B3%E6%8E%A7%E7%83%9F%E6%9C%89%E5%A4%9A%E6%8B%BC%23&amp;extparam=%23%E6%B7%B1%E5%9C%B3%E6%8E%A7%E7%83%9F%E6%9C%89%E5%A4%9A%E6%8B%BC%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#深圳控烟有多拼#</span></a> <a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4886899840712776" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">深圳卫健委的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/orj480/a8bfee30gy1hcnxtc6clhj20hs0a83zi.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/u0/si8c4ocFgx084pnf1nLO01041200EZp60E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=654x368.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1680685873&amp;ssig=hiiY6wYqvG&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/u0/Qgmtu3S7gx084pneITeg01041200Cp6Y0E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=638x360.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1680685873&amp;ssig=YWLF5miN